com.extensia.xcp.services.restapi.model.cardread

Class CardEdgeData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.extensia.xcp.services.restapi.model.cardread.CardEdgeData

  • public class CardEdgeData
extends java.lang.Object
    Class containing the data returned by the Card Read Service for a card edge. The enabled value indicates whether the card edge was enabled in the service configuration. The status value indicates the overall disposition of the card edge read results. Note that the same card edge, as indicated by the edgeType value, may occur more than once for card edge technologies such as HID iCLASS that support multiple card protocols.
